    "thumb1600": "https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/be/Odilon_Redon_-_The_Cyclops%2C_c._1914.jpg/1920px-Odilon_Redon_-_The_Cyclops%2C_c._1914.jpg",
